Belgium’s Leterme Says ‘Bad Bank’ Will Be Set Up for Dexia

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-10-04T20:16:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/belgium-s-leterme-says-bad-bank-will-be-set-up-for-dexia.html
A “bad bank” for troubled assets
will be set up for  Dexia SA (DEXB)  and will have government guarantees,
Belgian Prime Minister  Yves Leterme  said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
